    "More details on ADM1 is shown in Supplementary Note 3.",
    "The results in Fig. 2b showed the differences in composition distribution for the three main biogas production waste sources including carbohydrates, proteins, and lipids, with a negative correlation between carbohydrates and proteins and between carbohydrates and lipids in feedstocks.",
